rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Salvaging business not very strong in
Invidia, so things found in Avaritia
sell like hot cakes!

rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0002
rows.name:
On other hand, in Superbia, people
not really care about salvaged things.
Good food have more appeal there.

rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Meanwhile Avaritia Trade Guild free
to travel between countries, so it not
really matter either way to us.

rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Just take side of country that reap
biggest profit. That what Chairman
Bahn taught me!
